Frankly, I've given up trying.

00:18:04.650 --> 00:18:15.380
Just as Sarah obeyed Abraham, calling him Lord.

00:18:15.380 --> 00:18:22.380
Hebrews 11 and Isaiah 51 also cite Sarah as a fine example for Christian wives.

00:18:22.380 --> 00:18:28.380
But Christian husbands can also learn much from carefully examining.

00:18:28.380 --> 00:18:32.380
Sarah's example for me.

00:18:32.380 --> 00:18:51.259
