00:18:51.259 --> 00:19:05.720
A life fraught with danger and hardship.

00:19:05.720 --> 00:19:13.569
She unselfishly supported Abraham no matter what.

00:19:13.569 --> 00:19:35.740
Just like my Jessica, she does without, never complains.

00:19:35.740 --> 00:19:45.019
What a gem. I can do better, letting her know just how precious she is to me.

00:19:45.019 --> 00:20:08.279
Sarah submissively obeyed her husband.

00:20:08.279 --> 00:20:44.190
But she also spoke up. She loved her son.

00:20:44.190 --> 00:20:47.190
