00:20:47.190 --> 00:20:56.430
God's promises through Isaac, even though she knew it would upset Abraham.

00:20:56.430 --> 00:21:12.579
She spoke up.

00:21:12.579 --> 00:21:15.579
She must have thought carefully before speaking to him.

00:21:15.579 --> 00:21:20.140
