I needed to tell him how I felt.

00:21:49.769 --> 00:21:52.769
But I needed to do it the right way.

00:21:52.769 --> 00:21:58.230
That night, we spoke.

00:21:58.230 --> 00:22:07.710
And little by little, things started to improve.

00:22:07.710 --> 00:22:09.710
Imitating Sarah.

00:22:09.710 --> 00:22:11.710
Really worked.

